title: Couth Buzzard Espresso Buono
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Cafe, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe inside a book store. Serves vegan gluten free cookies, muffins, power bars and other snacks from the Flying Apron Bakery. Offers made-in-house vegan Amish friendship bread, soups that are sometimes vegan and personal sized vegan pizzas. Active community based calendar of events including live music, open mic nights and writer's group meetings.
